title: Omega Tradestation 2000i
description: The most popular program of the technical analysis. Package Omega Prosuite includes three programs: Omega Tradestation - the program for the technical analysis, Radar Screen - the program for the simultaneous analysis of set of tools, Option Station - the program for work with options. Includes last version of the given product with all updatings and Service pack, the instruction and all necessary for program installation. On program Omega Tradestation 2000 in the given archive it is applied Metaserver RT Pro - the program for transfer of quotations from any source supporting DDE in the programs of technical analysis Metastock and Omega Tradestation, and also in Microsoft Excel.
